          <div class="social-links">
            <h3>Let's Discuss</h3>
            <div class="social-grid">
              <a href="#" class="social-link">
                <span>‚òÅÔ∏è</span>
                <span>Cloud Architecture</span>
              </a>
              <a href="#" class="social-link">
                <span>üåê</span>
